    <title>EchoDitto Tech Blog: OS X 10.10 Yosemite Local Development Environment: Apache, PHP, and MySQL with Homebrew</title>
    <base href="http://echo.co/blog/os-x-1010-yosemite-local-development-environment-apache-php-and-mysql-homebrew">
